{"legislative_session": "20252026", "identifier": "AB570", "title": "Insurance: policy documents.", "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["bill"], "subject": ["Insurance", "policydocuments"], "abstracts": [{"note": "summary", "abstract": "Existing law generally regulates classes of insurance, including fire insurance. Existing law requires an insurer, after a covered loss under a fire insurance policy, to provide the insured a free copy of their policy within 30 calendar days of receiving a request from the insured. Existing law authorizes the Insurance Commissioner to extend this period.\n\nThis bill would require the insurer to provide the insured a free copy of their fire insurance policy within 15 calendar days of receiving a request from the insured."}], "other_titles": [], "other_identifiers": [], "actions": [{"description": "Read first time. To print.", "date": "2025-02-12", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["reading-1"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "From printer. May be heard in committee March 15.", "date": "2025-02-13", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Referred to Com. on INS.", "date": "2025-02-24", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["referral-committee"], "related_entities": [{"name": "Com. on INS.", "entity_type": "organization", "organization_id": null}]}, {"description": "From committee: Do pass and re-refer to Com. on APPR. with recommendation: To Consent Calendar. (Ayes 17. Noes 0.) (April 2). Re-referred to Com. on APPR.", "date": "2025-04-02", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["committee-passage", "committee-passage-favorable", "referral-committee"], "related_entities": [{"name": "Com. on APPR.", "entity_type": "organization", "organization_id": null}]}, {"description": "From committee: Do pass. 